      "body" : "This will throw a NullPointerException everytime. <code>city.getName()</code> and <code>&quot;N&#47;A&quot;</code> should be inverted. Ternary operators work like : <code>boolean_expression ? execute_if_true : execute_if_false</code> [<a href=\"https://www.baeldung.com/java-ternary-operator](documentation)\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">baeldung.com/java-ternary-operator](documentation)</a>"
