  "title" : "Short form for Java if statement",
  "body" : "<p>I know there is a way for writing a Java <code>if</code> statement in short form.</p>\n\n<pre><code>if (city.getName() != null) {\n    name = city.getName();\n} else {\n    name=\"N/A\";\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Does anyone know how to write the short form for the above 5 lines into one line?</p>\n"
